title: BREAKING NEWS: Real Madrid secure 33rd LaLiga title by beating Malaga

author: FourFourTwo
description: After Real Madrid claimed their first LaLiga title in five years, we look at five key matches behind their success under Zinedine Zidane.
title: Thrashing Betis and fightback at Villarreal – Five key matches in Real Madrid's LaLiga title triumph

author: talkSPORT
description: Goals from Cristiano Ronaldo and Karim Benzema swept Real Madrid to their first LaLiga title in five years as they cruised to a 2-0 win at Malaga on Sunday night. Needing just a point to confirm the crown in Zinedine Zidane's first full season in charge, Ronaldo settled any nerves when he fired home with just two minutes on the clock. And Benzema's second 10 minutes into the second half effectively sealed the title for Real, who still have the Champions League final against Juventus to come. Watch the goals below...
title: VIDEO: Malaga 0-2 Real Madrid: Cristiano Ronaldo on target as Los Blancos claim LaLiga title
